    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Museums dealing with the sea in general, navigation, or shipping, as distinct from "naval museums," which deal with navies, warships, or ships in general.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
